data.description: Back on the Market!  The buyer was unable to secure financing, making this your opportunity.  This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home has been remodeled giving a comfortable log cabin feel inside.  The large open kitchen features many beautiful knotty pine cabinets.  The floor plan would work great for hosting holiday gatherings.   The primary bedroom offers an en-suite with a big soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanity, and flows to the huge walk-in closet.  The deck features a canopy for shade.  There is a new shed large enough to handle all of your storage needs.  This property is ready for you to call home.
